{"tid":2498452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"右眼受傷少女就警方取其醫療報告 覆核上訴被潘兆初林文瀚區慶祥駁回","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T07:54:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3567ae5da44a8b52efb97c028b195aebcc08ea28","tid":2498452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5800&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=ba92c708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5800</a><br />\n<br />\n右眼受傷少女就警方取其醫療報告 覆核上訴被駁回<br />\n<br />\n【香港電台】前年在反修例示威中右眼受傷的女子，早前提出司法覆核，不滿警方申請法庭手令，取得她的醫療報告，並拒絕提供手令副本。她被判敗訴後提出上訴，上訴庭下午頒下書面判詞，駁回她的上訴。（原文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586917-20210421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586917-20210421.htm&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=c3050306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586917-20210421.htm&h=dc8da168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586917-20210421.htm</a> )<br />\n<br />\n📌 高等法院判決書（英文） <a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/CACV000033_2020.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2020%2FCACV000033_2020.docx&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=3c7a856e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/CACV000033_2020.docx</a><br />\n<br />\n#20210421新聞 #0811尖沙咀"},{"pid":"9fcc98062a207b42e6adb73bf8a8329f9005bfa5","tid":2498452,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac